      <title>达利奥（Dalio</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/dalio-warns-house-gop-of-debt-peril-as-lawmakers-weigh-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参加会议的议员说，布里奇沃特员工的创始人雷·达利奥（Ray Dalio）警告众议院共和党人有增加美国赤字的危险，并敦促他们控制支出。]]></description>
